    <item>
      <title>在新加坡最富有的家庭中，父子仇恨在危机中跌落180亿美元的Kwek Empire</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-27/what-s-behind-the-feud-in-singapore-s-richest-family-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡最大的开发商City Developments Ltd.陷入了危机，当时84岁的亿万富翁董事长Kwek Leng Beng对他的儿子（该公司首席执行官）提起诉讼，该公司据称策划了董事会政变。彭博记者分解了我们迄今为止对备受瞩目的争执吞没亚洲最富有的家庭的了解。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-27/what-s-behind-the-feud-in-singapore-s-richest-family-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 05:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅赛德斯将随着当地竞争的升温，将在中国裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/mercedes-set-to-cut-jobs-in-china-as-local-competition-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梅赛德斯 - 奔驰集团AG及其子公司正计划削减多达中国汽车制造商的15％的劳动力，主要是在其融资和销售部门内，因为德国制造商面临的两名知情人士都在加强世界上最大的汽车市场的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/mercedes-set-to-cut-jobs-in-china-as-local-competition-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 04:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰田的国内销售反弹，因为它从丑闻中恢复过来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/toyota-s-domestic-sales-rebound-as-it-recovers-from-scandals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丰田汽车公司（Toyota Motor Corp.）的一年在国外停滞不前的销售被日本的反弹抵消之后，它取得了缓慢而有前途的开局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/toyota-s-domestic-sales-rebound-as-it-recovers-from-scandals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 04:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本金属工会需求记录付费加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/japan-metal-worker-unions-demand-record-pay-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表制造商的日本主要工会表示，其成员正在寻求与雇主的年度谈判提高创纪录的工资，这是该国薪酬增长持续势头的早期迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/japan-metal-worker-unions-demand-record-pay-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 04:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
